{"tid":1648175,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"問責官員楊潤雄︰年青人不守法，學校、社會及父母有責任","createTime":"2019-10-12T05:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T15:09:10.000Z","uid":149494,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d90b75158c1eee1a6741e7c112a10eaeacf8a4ed","tid":1648175,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄指不應保護「跳閘」籲社會予學生正確價值觀<br />\n2019年10月12日 (12:00 下午)<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄強調不應將政治帶入校園<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄今早出席電台節目時表示，年輕人的被捕數字於開學後有上升趨勢，大部分為學生，情況令人擔憂。他指，<span style=\"color: red;\">學校應製造平和環境，不應將政治帶入校園。<br />\n<br />\n除了學校的教育，他認為父母及社會同樣重要，父母需教子女分辨是非對錯，而社會在守法方面應給予正確價值觀，例如年輕人在地鐵「跳閘」，員工執法卻遭不少成年人保護，質疑社會在守法上能否給予年輕人正確價值觀。</span><br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄亦指，年輕人互聯網上容易接觸到背景不詳人士，加上出現網上起底欺凌及假新聞泛濫，對年輕人的價值觀帶來很大衝擊，故正考慮向學校提供資源，以教導學生該如何接收及評估網上新聞。<br />\n<br />\n他提及理大專上學院講師陳偉強因言論而遭學生禁錮一事，他強調討論應要理性，學生應以理服人，而陳偉強被校方暫時調職並不安排其授課，他指出，若校方擔心學生容易有躁動情緒，而作出短期調動，並非懲罰，他會尊重院校的做法。<br />\n<br />\n社會目前氣氛緊張，不少示威者更出現破壞交通、地鐵等暴力事件，使市民生活帶來不便，他強調「互相尊重、包容」，各方都應停止暴力，再思考未來，不希望市民因近月修例事件而對政府失去信任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5233944-%E3%80%90%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E3%80%8C%E8%B7%B3%E9%96%98%E3%80%8D-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E7%B1%B2%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%88%E5%AD%B8?current_cat=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F5233944-%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E9%2596%2598%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BA%2588%25E5%25AD%25B8%3Fcurrent_cat%3D1&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKBUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=6175e8c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5233944-%E3%80%90%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E3%80%8C%E8%B7%B3%E9%96%98%E3%80%8D-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E7%B1%B2%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%88%E5%AD%B8?current_cat=1</a><br />\n<br />\n問責官員︰社會及父母有責任,學校也有責任,但政府同問責官員無責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f441a13a289940265c6e9f742c6d73197c4571","tid":1648175,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"得啦 WFC 5毛 垃圾Post沉啦 今日主線是TST"},{"pid":"e7c19500546685bb9654276b1c46e539b06cb5cb","tid":1648175,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94f441a13a289940265c6e9f742c6d73197c4571","tid":1648175,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"得啦 WFC 5毛 垃圾Post沉啦 今日主線是TST"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"嘩,幫政府洗地洗到咁出面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a5ecff39e46efd45d7a7009ae114dc684bf199","tid":1648175,"uid":973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:36:06.000Z","msg":"警察唔守法，咁係成個政府既責任啦"},{"pid":"c3dd8d7891a81633f5005663121b92e771c8f5fe","tid":1648175,"uid":199251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:37:22.000Z","msg":"問<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">責</span>官員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df4552e5d44589738967947bcd1bed316bba640","tid":1648175,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"政府都有責<br />\n係我無責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab7d8c4843ada459f4259f589487f88944e486a","tid":1648175,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"教育局無份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82f4c